OOC: sorry I think I missed posts again.  DIE DIE DIE AOL DIE.

::Aerotaur::
    He walks up to the bridge of the ship.  "Oh good Termitron's back.  And 
he brought a new friend.  Welcome aboard."

::Ender::
    He looks up again from his meditative state.  He does not wake up but 
walks to the door to wander somewhere aimless in his sleep.

OOC2: I don't know who's there so someone wake him up if anyone's there.
